# cxr 

Indexer and thesauri-based search application written in clojure

## Building

1. lein deps
2. lein compile
3. lein uberjar

## Running

Uberjar:

java -jar cxr-0.1-standalone.jar

Shell-wrapper: 

1. Install

$ lein install

2. Copy to PATH

$ cp ~/.lein/bin/cxr /usr/local/bin/

3. Run!

$ cxr # 

